snippet.title: Intellivision - PBA Bowling
snippet.description: Me playing PBA Bowling on the Intellivision. There are a lot of options in the game, including what hand you bowl with, how heavy your ball is, how slick the lane is, where your starting position is, and how you want to spin the ball. Pretty comprehensive really, and very satisfying when you come to grips with it.
